file.content:
openapi: 3.0.1
info:
  title: "ClickMatters integration API"
  description: |
    Click Matters API backend
  version: "0.1"
paths:
  /api/v1/players:
    post:
      operationId: syncPlayers
      tags:
        - player
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: "#/components/schemas/PlayersDTO"
        required: true
      responses:
        "201":
          description: record created
  /api/v1/activity:
    post:
      operationId: syncPlayerActivities
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/PlayerActivitiesDTO'
        required: true
      responses:
        "201":
          description: record created
  /api/v1/hello:
    get:
      operationId: hello
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                type: string
  /api/v1/hello/{id}:
    get:
      parameters:
        - name: id
          in: path
          description: affiliate id
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
        - name: foo
          in: query
          schema:
            type: string
        - name: bar
          in: query
          required: true
          schema:
            type: integer
        - name: baz
          in: header
          schema:
            type: string
          required: true
      operationId: hello
      responses:
        "200":
          description: OK
          content:
            '*/*':
              schema:
                type: string
components:
  schemas:
    PlayerDTO:
      type: object
      nullable: false
      properties:
        tag:
          type: string
        email:
          type: string
        user_id:
          type: string
        date_of_birth:
          type: string
          format: date
        first_name:
          type: string
        last_name:
          type: string
        nickname:
          type: string
        gender:
          type: string
          title: Gender
          enum:
            - m
            - f
            - "n"
        country:
          type: string
        language:
          type: string
        sign_up_at:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        duplicate:
          type: boolean
    PlayersDTO:
      type: object
      properties:
        players:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/PlayerDTO'
    DepositDTO:
      type: object
      properties:
        player:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PlayerDTO'
        playerenum:
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/PlayerEnum'
        deposit_id:
          type: string
        amount_cents:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        processed_at:
          type: string
          format: date-time
    PlayerActivitiesDTO:
      type: object
      properties:
        from:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        to:
          type: string
          format: date-time
        items:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/PlayerActivityDTO'
    PlayerActivityDTO:
      type: object
      properties:
        tag:
          type: string
        user_id:
          type: string
        currency:
          type: string
        bets_sum_cents:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        wager_cents:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        additional_deductions_sum_cents:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        rounds_count:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        bonus_issues_sum_cents:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        chargebacks_sum_cents:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        chargebacks_count:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        deposits_sum_cents:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        deposits_count:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        cashouts_sum_cents:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        cashouts_count:
          type: integer
          format: int64
        deposits:
          type: array
          items:
            $ref: '#/components/schemas/DepositDTO'
    PlayerEnum:
      enum:
        - good
        - bad
        - ugly
    'Parent':
      type: object
      properties:
        'vehicle':
          $ref: '#/components/schemas/Vehicle'
    #---------------------------------------------------------------------------
    # Abstract class with discriminator 'vehicle_type'
    #---------------------------------------------------------------------------
    'Vehicle':
      type: object
      nullable: false
      properties:
        'vehicle_type':
          type: string
      discriminator:
        propertyName: vehicle_type
        mapping:
          'CAR': '#/components/schemas/Car'
          'TRUCK': '#/components/schemas/Truck'
    #---------------------------------------------------------------------------
    # Concrete classes
    #---------------------------------------------------------------------------
    'Car':
      nullable: false
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Vehicle"
        - type: object
          properties:
            'car_property':
              type: string
    'Truck':
      nullable: false
      allOf:
        - $ref: "#/components/schemas/Vehicle"
        - type: object
          properties:
            'truck_property':
              type: string
